HEADWORD: Metapectin
<hw>Met`a*pec"tin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A substance obtained from, and resembling, pectin, and occurring in
overripe fruits.</def>⟦br⟧
